Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.23,0:01:45.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- I win!\N- I lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.80,0:01:48.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Fool! This is not a race!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.67,0:01:50.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Look Master Jaken!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.94,0:01:54.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just as Lord Sesshomaru said,\nthere's a dead demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.21,0:01:56.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My goodness, who could have...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.15,0:01:58.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It was Inuyasha.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.45,0:02:01.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Lord Sesshomaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.38,0:02:06.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Although... I don't think he got\naway unscathed either.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.99,0:02:13.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can smell it\non this demon's fangs...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.90,0:02:16.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The scent of Tetsusaiga.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.03,0:02:18.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just as I thought...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.73,0:02:21.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}these fangs broke Tetsusaiga apart.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.57,0:02:27.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Let us go.\N- Are you taking that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.81,0:02:29.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Silence, Rin.\NYou make too much noise.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.71,0:02:32.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.25,0:02:35.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I knew immediately\nwhat happened here...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.82,0:02:38.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}by the smell in the wind, but...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.65,0:02:40.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}one thing{\i0} - {\i1}what was it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.66,0:02:42.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The smell of Inuyasha's blood changed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.42,0:02:47.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's right{\i0} - {\i1}it was not the smell\nof a half-demon.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.73,0:02:50.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}It was the same smell as my blood\nand our father's.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.91,0:03:10.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}When Tetsusaiga was broken in two,\NI thought I was gonna die.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.89,0:03:12.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}When I said to myself\NI didn't want to die...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.05,0:03:14.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}my body started to get hot.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.62,0:03:17.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}And before I realized it,\NI had killed Goshinki.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.26,0:03:22.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}At that time, I felt something\NI never felt before...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.90,0:03:24.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}something strange.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.97,0:03:29.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I only felt pleasure at\ntearing apart Goshinki.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.37,0:03:31.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.31,0:03:33.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.44,0:03:34.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.54,0:03:35.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.64,0:03:37.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.25,0:03:40.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Moping over some broken sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.88,0:03:43.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My fish!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.96,0:03:55.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is the bull that belongs to Totosai,\nthe swordsmith who forged Tetsusaiga.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.63,0:03:56.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Only his bull?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.73,0:03:58.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Master Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.17,0:04:05.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Old Myoga!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.94,0:04:09.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Myoga! So you were\nhiding out at Totosai's?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.38,0:04:12.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How rude you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.81,0:04:14.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You ran away to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.58,0:04:15.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You ran away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.88,0:04:19.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Never mind that.\NMaster Inuyasha...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.19,0:04:20.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What happened to Tetsusaiga?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.96,0:04:22.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh... no!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.16,0:04:26.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This demon called Goshinki\nbit it in two.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.50,0:04:28.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I knew it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.56,0:04:32.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I came when I noticed that the scent of\NMaster Inuyasha's blood had changed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.80,0:04:37.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Master Inuyasha, you must take\nthe pieces of the sword...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.17,0:04:38.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and go to Master Totosai.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.54,0:04:42.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Does that mean the Tetsusaiga\ncan be repaired?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.34,0:04:43.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.41,0:04:46.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That bull will take you to\NTotosai.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.02,0:04:47.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.42,0:04:50.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, see ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.62,0:04:58.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Master Inuyasha really transformed?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.43,0:04:59.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.53,0:05:02.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Does that have anything to do\nwith Tetsusaiga being broken?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.90,0:05:03.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.33,0:05:09.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You know the Tetsusaiga is an heirloom\nleft to Master Inuyasha by his father.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.34,0:05:14.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Besides protecting Master Inuyasha\nfrom his enemies...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.24,0:05:17.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,it also serves to keep the demon\nside of him sealed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.78,0:05:21.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Seal the demon side of him?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.28,0:05:25.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The Tetsusaiga being broken means\NInuyasha will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.42,0:05:30.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yet the strong desire to live...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.89,0:05:34.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,awakened the demon's blood\nwhich flows through him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.93,0:05:38.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Once awakened, even if\nthe Tetsusaiga is repaired...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.40,0:05:44.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,that part of him will be\nharder to control.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.17,0:05:48.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He has tasted the pleasure of\nslaying an enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.71,0:05:53.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Does that mean Inuyasha's heart\nis becoming a demon's?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.08,0:05:56.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Y-you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.06,0:06:06.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.40,0:06:20.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh you... are such a fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.44,0:06:26.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Look what you did to\nmy dear, dear Tetsusaiga.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.15,0:06:27.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Will you shaddup?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.88,0:06:30.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Instead of bawling,\nhurry and fix my sword, old fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.92,0:06:33.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You young punk!\NYou think it's so easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.79,0:06:35.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Can't you fix it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.82,0:06:38.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're speaking to Totosai!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.33,0:06:41.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I can put it back in three days\nand three nights.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.93,0:06:43.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,However, I need something\nto bond it with.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.33,0:06:45.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Bond?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.63,0:06:47.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha, open your mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.04,0:06:50.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.35,0:07:00.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, I guess this fang will do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.62,0:07:01.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What're you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.08,0:07:06.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Silence! Your fang will\ngrow back in half a day!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.92,0:07:10.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn you are such a pain in the neck!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.13,0:07:13.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Make sure you bring it to me\nfixed in three days!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.56,0:07:16.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why three days?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.50,0:07:19.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You just said you can fix it in\nthree days and three nights!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.60,0:07:23.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Cripes! I'm counting on ya, old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.41,0:07:25.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.41,0:07:27.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,All right... you can look forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.50,0:07:49.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.97,0:07:53.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You are Kaijinbo?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.00,0:07:56.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Because you created too many\ndeviant swords...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.04,0:08:00.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,you were banished by your\nmaster, Totosai.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.51,0:08:03.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Totosai, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.61,0:08:05.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Haven't heard that name\nin quite a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.68,0:08:07.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,but it still makes my blood boil.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.78,0:08:10.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, Kaijinbo?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.55,0:08:14.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Would you like to forge a sword\nout of that demon's fangs?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.99,0:08:18.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't joke!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.39,0:08:21.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No way can I make a sword\nout of something that's dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.90,0:08:29.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is Lord Sesshomaru going to use\nthe Tenseiga, the sword of healing?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.64,0:08:34.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can see...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.94,0:08:36.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}the messengers from the\nnetherworld.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.96,0:08:51.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wow, this is totally different\nfrom earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.19,0:08:54.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kaijinbo, let me tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.76,0:08:59.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This sword, the Tenseiga, was forged\nby the master who banished you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.17,0:09:01.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And the fangs of that demon...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.30,0:09:06.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,broke the Tetsusaiga, a sword\nalso forged by Totosai.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.68,0:09:11.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Amazing. These fangs will make\na most powerful sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.08,0:09:18.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Tetsusaiga should be repaired\nby tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.75,0:09:22.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But this all happened at such\na bad time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.56,0:09:23.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The night of the new moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.56,0:09:29.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn it all! Totosai is late!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.26,0:09:33.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's just like a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.40,0:09:36.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You didn't know, Sango?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.70,0:09:40.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I only heard about it,\nand it's the first time I'm seeing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.88,0:09:44.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Half-demons like Inuyasha\nhave one night...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.75,0:09:48.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,when they lose their demon powers\nand become mere mortals.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.02,0:09:51.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,See, he doesn't have fangs, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.32,0:09:53.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Interesting, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.55,0:09:56.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku, you're having fun with this,\naren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.06,0:09:58.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You figured it out?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.03,0:10:02.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If attacked by an enemy on this night,\nhe can be killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.56,0:10:04.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hence, the night of new moon\nwhen Inuyasha...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.10,0:10:07.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ioses his demon powers\nmust be kept strictly secret!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.67,0:10:10.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So how do you know about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.34,0:10:14.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shippo, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.94,0:10:17.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stop, Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.38,0:10:20.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You blabbermouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.08,0:10:23.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stop! I didn't mean any harm!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.85,0:10:26.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You better not have\nintended harm!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.02,0:10:27.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.39,0:10:34.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How come more and more people\nknow about my secret?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.40,0:10:35.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.16,0:10:39.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It means you have more\npeople concerned about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.97,0:10:47.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Still when I turn mortal...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.64,0:10:49.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't stand this feeling\nof unease.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.98,0:10:54.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}When I become a full-fledged demon,\nit'll be good riddance to these feelings.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.65,0:10:56.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.18,0:11:00.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But if I become a full-fledged demon...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.35,0:11:02.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kagome and the others will{\i0} be...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.42,0:11:03.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.16,0:11:09.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't stray too far from us tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.96,0:11:11.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hah! Be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.60,0:11:16.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Even I have times when\NI want to think by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.51,0:11:18.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.51,0:11:23.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha, do you still want to\nbecome a full-fledged demon?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.35,0:11:26.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.45,0:11:27.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I was scared that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.02,0:11:30.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What're you saying!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.49,0:11:33.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If I hadn't transformed that time...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.82,0:11:37.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,you'd all have been killed\nby that Goshinki!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.63,0:11:39.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't mean that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.89,0:11:43.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's not the face that changed,\nor how scared I felt.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.53,0:11:45.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Was I that scary-looking?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.27,0:11:51.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I just... felt like your heart was\nbeyond my reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.64,0:11:58.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That you were going to forget\nabout me... and that scared me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.85,0:12:01.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}That time...\nwhen I transformed...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.05,0:12:03.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}My heart was...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.65,0:12:06.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you crazy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.09,0:12:09.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No matter what happens,\NI'm still me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.06,0:12:13.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I wouldn't forget about you\nor Miroku and the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.33,0:12:20.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't ever forget.\NPlease, Inuyasha!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.77,0:12:24.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kaijinbo!\NIt's been three days!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.24,0:12:28.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Have you forged a sword from\nthe demon's fangs?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.85,0:12:39.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's done!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.05,0:12:42.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A magnificent demon sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.57,0:12:55.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This must be Kaijinbo's doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.95,0:13:18.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I was slain by Kaijinbo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.63,0:13:21.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.46,0:13:22.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's go, Jaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.80,0:13:24.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hurry and put your body back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.00,0:13:26.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Lord Sesshomaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.14,0:13:32.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Did you perhaps use Tenseiga\nto bring me back to life?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.67,0:13:36.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Who else besides me\nis capable of such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.71,0:13:39.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No one... Lord Sesshomaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.91,0:13:42.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Did Kaijinbo finish the sword?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.35,0:13:44.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Y-yes, he did.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.52,0:13:48.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kaijinbo claimed that he\nhad forged the demon sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.36,0:13:52.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But his eyes looked so strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.29,0:13:56.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Like... Like he was possessed\nby the sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.46,0:13:59.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hmm... I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.41,0:14:08.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha, why don't you get\nsome sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.58,0:14:09.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.71,0:14:11.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.38,0:14:15.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I never sleep\nwhen I take on the human form!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.05,0:14:18.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you too scared to sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.62,0:14:19.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.82,0:14:23.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm so scared!\NSo what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.39,0:14:24.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Good to be honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.76,0:14:27.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I have a lot of enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.93,0:14:30.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If I'm attacked when I'm like this,\NI don't have a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.17,0:14:34.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, it's a good lesson for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.50,0:14:38.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku, do you sense it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.94,0:14:41.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A very powerful aura.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.30,0:15:06.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Which one of you is Inuyasha!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.64,0:15:08.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.11,0:15:14.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I am Kaijinbo.\NA master swordsmith.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.48,0:15:15.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Swordsmith?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.08,0:15:18.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This sword which I forged\nnamed Tokijin...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.15,0:15:23.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,is crying for a taste of\nthe blood of Inuyasha.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.42,0:15:25.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}This swordsmith,\nwhy is he after me?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.92,0:15:31.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hmm... so you are Inuyasha?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.43,0:15:33.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This sword has told me so.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.53,0:15:35.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,D-damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.73,0:15:38.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why, I thought you were some demon.\NBut you're just a mortal.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.70,0:15:43.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha, can you think of any\nreason why he begrudges you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.50,0:15:44.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,None...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.77,0:15:45.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Heard that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.17,0:15:50.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,As I told you,\nthis sword wants to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.41,0:15:56.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This Tokijin was forged from\nthe fangs of the demon...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.72,0:16:00.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,who broke the Tetsusaiga,\nthe sword created by old Totosai.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.76,0:16:03.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Made from the fangs of Goshinki...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.56,0:16:05.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,the demon who broke\nthe Tetsusaiga in half!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.89,0:16:08.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So it's a sword filled with the\nhate of Goshinki.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.53,0:16:12.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm tired of listening to\nyour jabbering!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.70,0:16:14.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just come and attack, Kaijinbo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.97,0:16:16.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll turn you into mincemeat!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.84,0:16:19.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stay back, Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.17,0:16:21.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let me and Sango handle this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.01,0:16:24.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There's no way you can win,\nthe way you are now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.24,0:16:25.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha, bear with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.35,0:16:28.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hiraikotsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.09,0:16:33.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Where are you aiming?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.77,0:16:46.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The Hiraikotsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.24,0:16:56.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.44,0:16:58.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Without a doubt, it is\na formidable sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.05,0:17:01.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well then... I have no choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.72,0:17:06.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Heaven's punishment!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.23,0:17:14.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.29,0:17:17.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I thought the Wind Tunnel was\NMiroku's only legitimate weapon, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.50,0:17:19.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,he {\i1}has{\i0} spiritual powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.97,0:17:26.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Watch out, Miroku!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.58,0:17:39.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Tokijin... you are amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.79,0:17:42.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The ultimate sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.36,0:17:46.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The enemy is not Kaijinbo...\nit's the sword!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.16,0:17:49.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Playtime's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.00,0:17:52.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,His head is split in two,\nyet he's acting as if nothing happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.00,0:17:54.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's almost like...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.87,0:17:57.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,he's being controlled by\NTokijin the sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.34,0:18:00.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Come at me, Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.61,0:18:03.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Or are you so afraid that\nyou can't move?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.54,0:18:06.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hiding meekly by the girl and child!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.92,0:18:11.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha, don't be lured\nby those words!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.52,0:18:14.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hah! I'm not that stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.66,0:18:15.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.96,0:18:18.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,it's me that he's come after.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.16,0:18:22.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I {\i1}will not{\i0} hide nor run!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.26,0:18:23.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.10,0:18:26.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's such a simpleton!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.31,0:18:37.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Totosai!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.64,0:18:39.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is Tetsusaiga repaired?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.35,0:18:42.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh dear... I wondered what all\nthe noise was about.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.72,0:18:44.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Totosai, you're late!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.09,0:18:46.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Give it here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.22,0:18:49.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No, Master Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.92,0:18:50.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Old Myoga!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.19,0:18:53.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Tetsusaiga will not transform...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.19,0:18:56.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,when wielded by a human who\nhas lost his demon powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.23,0:18:58.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kaijinbo, it's been a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.27,0:19:01.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you still alive, Totosai?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.14,0:19:04.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You've crafted yet another\nawful sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.77,0:19:06.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What is that evil aura?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.71,0:19:08.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Totosai...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.94,0:19:13.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll show you who is the\nbetter swordsmith.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.81,0:19:17.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Master Totosai!\NYou know Kaijinbo?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.22,0:19:19.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes, he's a former pupil...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.65,0:19:21.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,One I banished long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.92,0:19:28.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He killed ten children in order\nto create a sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.86,0:19:31.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He smothered the blade with\nhuman blood and oil...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.73,0:19:33.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,in order to make it\nseethe with hatred.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.20,0:19:35.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Draw your sword, Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.17,0:19:40.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll crush that sword before the\nvery eyes of old Totosai!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.14,0:19:45.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No sense going easy on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.38,0:19:51.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Totosai! You'd better have made the\NTetsusaiga even stronger than before!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.39,0:19:53.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A little.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.82,0:19:55.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That won't do!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.26,0:19:59.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That sword is made from the fangs of\nthe demon that broke the Tetsusaiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.34,0:20:11.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.28,0:20:17.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is it for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.59,0:20:29.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm relieved, Tetsusaiga.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.86,0:20:31.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You seem to be a bit\nmore powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.09,0:20:33.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's not broken!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.39,0:20:35.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.36,0:20:37.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But Inuyasha is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.37,0:20:41.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hah! Before the sword breaks,\nyour body will break.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.84,0:20:43.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Too bad, Kaijinbo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.34,0:20:46.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll admit that sword of yours\nis pretty strong...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.07,0:20:48.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But you're not good enough\nto handle it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.71,0:20:52.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You should've killed me\nin one sweep.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.45,0:21:00.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Before this happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.42,0:21:02.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's transforming!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.02,0:21:03.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Dawn is breaking!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.89,0:21:10.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm gonna test the Tetsusaiga's\nnew blade on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.77,0:21:24.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Totosai! What'd you do\nto my Tetsusaiga?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.01,0:21:27.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Answer, Totosai!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.41,0:21:29.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What'd you do to the Tetsusaiga!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.15,0:21:32.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hmmm? You having problems?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.05,0:21:34.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shaddup!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.15,0:21:36.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's super heavy! What'd you do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.92,0:21:41.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, that's from the fang I used\nas a bond.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.50,0:21:42.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.16,0:21:46.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hah! No use having a sword\nyou can't even hold!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.60,0:21:49.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll slice you in half along\nwith your sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.14,0:21:54.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Raise your sword or you'll die!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.44,0:21:55.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How can you be so unreasonable?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.78,0:21:58.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,D-damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.59,0:23:50.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Tokijin, a sword filled with\NGoshinki's hatred...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.46,0:23:52.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,possesses the swordsmith Kaijinbo.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.49,0:23:55.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,With unusual powers,\nit attacks Inuyasha.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.00,0:23:57.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then the true owner appears!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.23,0:24:00.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,As though trying to test something...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.27,0:24:04.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sesshomaru, Inuyasha's brother,\nturns Tokijin on Inuyasha.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.40,0:24:07.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagura, Naraku's incarnation,\napproaches Sesshomaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.48,0:24:12.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Next on Inuyasha:\N"Sesshomaru Wields Tokijin!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.88,0:24:13.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't miss it!
